{{#if subscription_active}}

<div class="dash_content">
   <h3>{{dashboard_page_name}} - Coming Soon</h3>
   <p>
      Our goal is to provide content creators with a platform that helps eliminate the difficulty of making a business through content.
      We are currently working on creating systems that build you websites, manage all forms of content, and automate your marketing.
      We'll have monetization options as well such as selling or affiliating products, recieving ad revenue, and membership abilities.
      <br />
      <br />
      <strong>Creating a business is hard, but we'll make it easy for you.</strong>
   </p>
   {{#if user.completed_onboard_payouts}}
     {{#if stripe_connected_account_link}}
     <a target="_blank" style="margin: 25px 0; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px;" class="dash_stripe_btn" href="{{stripe_connected_account_link}}">View Stripe Account Dashboard</a>
     {{/if}}
   {{/if}}
</div>

{{else}}

<div class="dash_content">
   <h3>Subscription is no longer active.</h3>
   <p>
      We're sorry but this subscription is no longer active. This issue can arise due to a failed payment, or a paused/canceled subscription.
      If you're looking to renew your subscription, go to the customer portal located in dashboard settings.
   </p>
</div>

{{/if}}
